  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Women4Women Mobile Platform</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. To develop and test an Information Communication Technicology (ICT) women farmers&apos; information system that incorporates a data collection platform that enables field data collection through self reporting by beneficiaries or through independent enumerators.  2. Trading platform where input suppliers and buyers can be brought together to provide services to farmers  - Extension services, marketing prices, weather information 3. A system that empowers farmers especially women to collect information on their farming needs, track public performance policies (for instance, GES, NIRSAL, Insurance...) 4. Provides GIS services to locate farmers and possibly store and retrieve information about them</narrative>
  </description>
